result.name: Din Tai Fung

reviews.text: Din Tai Fung is simply the best Korean restaurant I have ever eaten!  The service is super fast, the restaurant is really big, everything is very clean, the waiters are welcoming and attentive to our needs.  the restaurant has even one Michelin star.  go there it's a delight!

Tasty food with low prices. I didn't waited at all, almost instantly was seated and food was delivered in 3 minutes. Dim Sam's are good but not crazy, beef soup was too spicy and nothing special. Stuff doesn't speak in English and not friendly. If you want to eat good food with low prices it's good choice. But didn't understand the Michelin taste :) Extremely noisy.

Excellent food and atmosphere. Didn't feel at all like a Michelin starred restaurant like we'd expect at home. It was .ore laid back and relaxed. Food was excellent. Maybe a little noisy due to other diners, but great service and choice of food. Would return

The steamed pork dumplings here is the best. The other dumplings tastes very good too. You should not miss here if you are a fan of dumplings.
The mushroom soup worths to try if you like mushrooms. It brings the best out from different kind of mushrooms.
This place is so so good. The food is amazing. Some of the best dim sum I've ever had. Really worth a visit if you're in Hong Kong

reviews.text: 好吃😋服務好👍

Din Tai Fung is simply the best Korean restaurant I have ever eaten!  The service is super fast, the restaurant is really big, everything is very clean, the waiters are welcoming and attentive to our needs.  the restaurant has even one Michelin star.  go there it's a delight!
貴為米之連推介食肆，味道固然不錯 ，食物點心價格當然亦不平宜，但份量嚴太少，細細碟，2-3個人食起碼叫6-7碟才夠，最後埋單至少都$4-500，唔太低食，繁忙時間好多人排隊，尤其好多外藉人士，因此要等位等好耐，値唔値得去真的見人見至，但服務確係好，職員有禮貌。

Tasty food with low prices. I didn't waited at all, almost instantly was seated and food was delivered in 3 minutes. Dim Sam's are good but not crazy, beef soup was too spicy and nothing special. Stuff doesn't speak in English and not friendly. If you want to eat good food with low prices it's good choice. But didn't understand the Michelin taste :) Extremely noisy.
